@host = http://localhost:5002

### Health check
GET {{host}}/health

### Test Universitas Client
GET {{host}}/test/universitas/cdfecc4c-e651-401e-95ad-79e8547f3230

## Preview
POST {{host}}/api/homologations/preview
Content-Type: application/json
